{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place hazelnuts and dried apricots into mixing bowl and chop <b>5-10 sec\/speed 5<b>, or until roughly chopped (see Tip). Transfer into a large bowl and set aside.","Place onions, garlic, oil and salt into mixing bowl and chop <b>6 sec\/speed 4.5<b>, then sauté <b>13 min\/120°C\/speed <b>.","Add couscous and stock paste and stir <b>10 sec\/\/speed 2<b>.","Add 200 g of the water, stir using spatula, cover with mixing bowl lid and allow couscous to absorb liquid for 5 minutes. Meanwhile, place simmering basket onto mixing bowl lid and weigh carrot, zucchini, red capsicum and green peas into it and set aside.","Transfer soaked couscous into large bowl containing chopped nuts and apricots. Add 150 g of the feta and stir gently to mix well. Spread a quarter of the couscous mixture loosely into Varoma dish, leaving some holes unobstructed so steam can circulate, and remaining couscous onto Varoma tray. Place 400 g water into mixing bowl and insert simmering basket with vegetables. Place Varoma into position, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>17 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>.","Transfer couscous onto a large serving dish and gently fluff the couscous using a fork. Drizzle steamed vegetables with 1 tbsp oil and stir gently to coat. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and arrange vegetables around the couscous. Serve hot, garnished with chopped parsley (optional) and reserved feta cheese."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["150 g hazelnuts","150 g dried apricots","300 g brown onion, cut into quarters","20 g garlic cloves","60 g olive oil, plus extra for drizzling","½ tsp salt","200 g couscous","1 heaped tsp Vegetable stock paste (refer to the recipe in The Basic Cookook)","600 g water","200 g carrots, cut into slices (5 mm)","200 g zucchini, cut into slices (7-10 mm)","150 g red capsicum, cut into pieces (2-3 cm)","100 g frozen green peas","200 g feta cheese, cut into small cubes (5 mm)","2 tsp fresh flat-leaf parsley, chopped, for garnishing (optional)"]}],"id":"r156346","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-W3-ApiKyAFM\/XZVRvQmKBII\/AAAAAAAAdSc\/y2k82mjtVzAsuTphbpiumloV0Unox_i6wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_vldmWrNnBQHfUQxZ.png","title":"Couscous with apricots, hazelnuts and feta, mixed vegetables","publishedAt":"2017-05-08T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"18 g","fat":"37 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"47 g","calories":"2607 kJ \/ 622 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl","hintsAndTricks":["Dried apricots when soft take as little as <b>5 seconds<b> to chop with the hazelnuts; however, if very dry and tough, they can take up to <b>15 seconds.<b>","Add pistachios and\/or pomegranate seeds as extra garnishes.<br>- Replace half or all the couscous with quinoa for a slightly nutty flavour and a higher protein content."],"basicInfo":["medium","45m","1h 15m","6 portions"]}